languages.text: "Пусть для прочих я — бездомный в подземелье. В моем сознании — тысячи миров и жизней!"
"The rest may see me as a homeless slob who lives underground. But my mind houses thousands of worlds and lives!"

languages.text: “或许在别人眼中，我只不过是个住在地下、无家可归的流浪汉，但我的头脑里装着成千上万的世界与生命！”

languages.text: «Los demás me ven como un vago sintecho que vive en el subsuelo, pero ¡en mi mente hay miles de mundos y vidas!».
languages.original_text: "The rest may see me as a homeless slob who lives underground. But my mind houses thousands of worlds and lives!"

languages.text: 「他人から見りゃ、俺は地下に住むだらしないホームレスかもしれねえ。だがね、俺の頭ん中には数えきれないほどの世界と命が宿ってんだ！」
languages.original_text: "The rest may see me as a homeless slob who lives underground. But my mind houses thousands of worlds and lives!"

traits.locale_text: 「他人から見りゃ、俺は地下に住むだらしないホームレスかもしれねえ。だがね、俺の頭ん中には数えきれないほどの世界と命が宿ってんだ！」

languages.text: "Für die anderen mag ich ein obdachloser Schmutzfink sein, der unter der Erde lebt. Aber in meinem Geist wohnen Tausende von Welten und Leben!"
languages.original_text: "The rest may see me as a homeless slob who lives underground. But my mind houses thousands of worlds and lives!"

languages.text: « Les autres me voient peut-être comme un immonde clochard qui vit sous terre, mais mon esprit abrite des milliers de mondes et de vies ! »

languages.text: "Birçokları beni yerin altında yaşayan, evsiz bir mikrop olarak görebilir ama zihnimde ne dünyalar ne hayatlar barınıyor!"

traits.locale_text: "Birçokları beni yerin altında yaşayan, evsiz bir sersem olarak görebilir ama zihnimde yüzlerce dünya ve yaşamı besliyorum!"
